rows.label: tlk00000593_01_msg0001
rows.name:
I wonder if this was a playground for the
people who lived in Eden.

rows.label: tlk00000593_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Though I don't know how to play
with any of this...

rows.label: tlk00000593_01_msg0101
rows.name: How do you use this thing?

rows.label: tlk00000593_01_msg0102
rows.name: Is it for training your body?

rows.label: tlk00000593_01_msg0201
rows.name: Mo-mo-mo? What is this place for, Mo-mo?

rows.label: tlk00000593_01_msg0202
rows.name: Is it a place where Drivers train, Mo-mo?

rows.label: tlk00000593_01_msg0302
rows.name:
These are all things not found
in the records of Alst.

rows.label: tlk00000593_01_msg0402
rows.name:
Nothing here is made of wood.
It's all incredibly sturdy stuff.
